data.description: Welcome to this exquisite home nestled in the heart of Mahtomedi!  This charming home effortlessly combines modern comforts with timeless elegance, offering a perfect blend of functionality and style.  Boasting a thoughtfully designed floor plan, this property features spacious living areas, a gourmet kitchen, and vaulted ceilings.  The attention to detail is evident throughout, from the gleaming hardwood floors to the tastefully appointed finishes.  The lower level unveils a flexible space, ripe with potential - could be used as a third bedroom.  Outside, the fenced yard beckons relaxation and social gatherings, while the deck provides an ideal setting for dining or cherished moments with loved ones.  Nestled in a sought-after neighborhood and a top-rated school district, seize the opportunity to make this extraordinary property your new home!
